        <Parent_String>weighing devices by function [300196295], weighing devices [300195708], measuring devices for forces [300195702], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
